text: George Sibley may refer to: * George Sibley Johns (1857–1941), American journalist * George Sibley (Six Feet Under), a character in the TV series Six Feet Under * George C. Sibley (1782–1863), American explorer, soldier, Indian agent, politician, and educator * George Sibley (1942–2005), common law husband of American convicted murderer Lynda Lyon Block
